 incredible events\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 733}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There have been so many incredible performances by the Chinese team and all the athletes in Paris.\\\"\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 834, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 790, \"end\": 797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.6029388942015018, \"rank\": 0.658452953059183, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 827, \"end\": 832, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999863885024, \"rank\": 1.3611401977610647e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so many incredible performances\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 782}, {\"ngram\": \"all the athletes\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 823}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Particularly impressed by the women's synchronized diving and the swimming medley relay, both in which China won gold, Gu has been taking notes from the sidelines as a spectator.\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 1014, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 939, \"end\": 944, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999442516597239, \"rank\": 3.04062272693702e-05, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the women's synchronized diving\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 893}, {\"ngram\": \"the swimming medley relay\", \"from\": 898, \"to\": 923}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 949, \"to\": 953}, {\"ngram\": \"Gu\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 957}, {\"ngram\": \"notes\", \"from\": 974, \"to\": 979}, {\"ngram\": \"the sidelines\", \"from\": 985, \"to\": 998}, {\"ngram\": \"a spectator\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1013}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On August 10, Gu will participate in the public Paris 2024 marathon with around 20,000 people who want to push their limits to those of Olympic athletes.\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1064, \"end\": 1074, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999999999235115, \"rank\": 7.648901936695195e-10, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1025}, {\"ngram\": \"Gu\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1032}, {\"ngram\": \"marathon\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1083}, {\"ngram\": \"around 20,000 people\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1109}, {\"ngram\": \"their limits\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1139}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic athletes\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1168}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The event will follow the same route and is scheduled for the same day as the official Olympics marathon.\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1275, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The event\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1179}, {\"ngram\": \"the same route\", \"from\": 1192, \"to\": 1206}, {\"ngram\": \"the same day\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1240}, {\"ngram\": \"the official Olympics marathon\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1274}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The only hurdle is, she's never run a marathon before.\", \"from\": 1276, \"to\": 1330, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The only hurdle\", \"from\": 1276, \"to\": 1291}, {\"ngram\": \"a marathon\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1322}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Eileen Gu enjoyed the opening ceremony./ Dylan Martinez/Reuters After accepting the invitation with a few weeks' notice, the Olympic champion turned to the world for advice: \\\"I looked online for a three-week marathon program and the only thing I saw was 'do not!'\\\"\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1597, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1332, \"end\": 1341, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eileen_Gu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Eileen Gu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eileen_Gu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eileen_Gu\"}, {\"begin\": 1373, \"end\": 1378, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Dylan\", \"score\": 0.9999973496927501, \"rank\": 1.7441143827169111e-06, \"text\": \"Dylan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Dylan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Dylan\"}, {\"begin\": 1379, \"end\": 1387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isaiah_Martinez\", \"score\": 0.9621683608108567, \"rank\": 0.03931895376503675, \"text\": \"Martinez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isaiah_Martinez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isaiah_Martinez\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony./\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1372}, {\"ngram\": \"/Reuters\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1395}, {\"ngram\": \"the invitation\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1426}, {\"ngram\": \"a few weeks' notice\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1451}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic champion\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1473}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1484, \"to\": 1493}, {\"ngram\": \"advice\", \"from\": 1498, \"to\": 1504}, {\"ngram\": \"a three-week marathon program\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1556}, {\"ngram\": \"the only thing\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1575}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, watching her fellow athletes at the Games has helped her see competing from another perspective, particularly as she prepares for the longest distance she's ever run.\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1774, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her fellow athletes\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1636}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1649}, {\"ngram\": \"another perspective\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1703}, {\"ngram\": \"the longest distance\", \"from\": 1738, \"to\": 1758}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think watching as a spectator has really made me take note of how much the competition is mental,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 1776, \"to\": 1888, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a spectator\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1808}, {\"ngram\": \"note\", \"from\": 1833, \"to\": 1837}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 1865}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It really is performing when it counts under pressure on that day.\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1956, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 1943}, {\"ngram\": \"that day\", \"from\": 1947, \"to\": 1955}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not the day before, not the day after, but really on the day that it counts peaking at the right time.\\\"\", \"from\": 1957, \"to\": 2060, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Not the day before, not the day\", \"from\": 1957, \"to\": 1988}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 2010, \"to\": 2017}, {\"ngram\": \"peaking\", \"from\": 2033, \"to\": 2040}, {\"ngram\": \"the right time\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2058}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whether it's perfecting a forward double cork or running her first ever marathon, Gu turns to one golden rule for winning: \\\"I have a saying for myself that I train like I have never won and I compete like I have never lost.\\\"\", \"from\": 2062, \"to\": 2286, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a forward double cork\", \"from\": 2086, \"to\": 2107}, {\"ngram\": \"Gu\", \"from\": 2144, \"to\": 2146}, {\"ngram\": \"one golden rule\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2171}, {\"ngram\": \"a saying\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2201}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When it comes to competing on the day, the Olympic ski champion says she is able to \\\"switch\\\" into this mentality.\", \"from\": 2288, \"to\": 2401, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"f